::Orchestra/Composer/Symphony::

     Orchestra smiled and stood up off the chair.

     "You're right, it didn't.  So, what else do we have to do?" Orchestra
asked.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
      Composer arrived at the Iron Fist.  He landed and entered, carrying a
bunch of pieces from his pod, as well as others that he put in his
compartment.

      "Leader...Zardus.....I.........got...some........stuff........."
Composer said through comm-link, trying to hold everything he had.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
       Symphony walked around Maximal City, and into the training room.  He
ran over to IR.

       "Can I train?" he asked in his little voice.
